  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Building A Blueprint Deck</h2>You can build a set of building blueprints according to your own preference, and according to the different characteristics of each race, which is the most suitable for the passage of the game. Building blueprints will appear randomly during the game for players to choose and use.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/91c867c15bd445efac0ab20189651b7f.poster.avif?t=1718959856\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/91c867c15bd445efac0ab20189651b7f.webm?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/91c867c15bd445efac0ab20189651b7f.mp4?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Develop Village</h2>During the game, after each wave of enemy attack, you can choose two building blueprints to build your village. You can choose different building sequences according to your preference, for example, you can build more defense towers to protect your village first, or you can upgrade your warrior guild to increase the strength of your trained warriors. Whether or not your village can survive depends on your wisdom.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/37a444e94202a041dfef41355e961a30.poster.avif?t=1718959856\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/37a444e94202a041dfef41355e961a30.webm?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/37a444e94202a041dfef41355e961a30.mp4?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Produce Food And Materials</h2>Once the village population starts to increase, the amount of food consumed will also increase. You must carefully control the demand and supply of food, or else you may cause a large number of villagers to starve and instantly wipe out the village. In addition to food, you must also produce the materials needed to equip the guards. Use the various workshops to create weapons, defenses, and accessories for your guards to give them more power.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/0e9ff18b4c0fb2a3b1dd72c3d28682ec.poster.avif?t=1718959856\" width=630 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/0e9ff18b4c0fb2a3b1dd72c3d28682ec.webm?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/0e9ff18b4c0fb2a3b1dd72c3d28682ec.mp4?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Training Guards</h2>There are four types of guards to train: Warrior, Bowman, Wizard, and Priest. Each type of guard has its own specialty, and you can win by matching different types of guards to maximize your defense.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/ef915e306e7641559bec449a4d638fb9.poster.avif?t=1718959856\" width=640 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/ef915e306e7641559bec449a4d638fb9.webm?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/ef915e306e7641559bec449a4d638fb9.mp4?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Building A Blueprint Deck</h2>You can build a set of building blueprints according to your own preference, and according to the different characteristics of each race, which is the most suitable for the passage of the game. Building blueprints will appear randomly during the game for players to choose and use.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/91c867c15bd445efac0ab20189651b7f.poster.avif?t=1718959856\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/91c867c15bd445efac0ab20189651b7f.webm?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/91c867c15bd445efac0ab20189651b7f.mp4?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Develop Village</h2>During the game, after each wave of enemy attack, you can choose two building blueprints to build your village. You can choose different building sequences according to your preference, for example, you can build more defense towers to protect your village first, or you can upgrade your warrior guild to increase the strength of your trained warriors. Whether or not your village can survive depends on your wisdom.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/37a444e94202a041dfef41355e961a30.poster.avif?t=1718959856\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/37a444e94202a041dfef41355e961a30.webm?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/37a444e94202a041dfef41355e961a30.mp4?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Produce Food And Materials</h2>Once the village population starts to increase, the amount of food consumed will also increase. You must carefully control the demand and supply of food, or else you may cause a large number of villagers to starve and instantly wipe out the village. In addition to food, you must also produce the materials needed to equip the guards. Use the various workshops to create weapons, defenses, and accessories for your guards to give them more power.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/0e9ff18b4c0fb2a3b1dd72c3d28682ec.poster.avif?t=1718959856\" width=630 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/0e9ff18b4c0fb2a3b1dd72c3d28682ec.webm?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/0e9ff18b4c0fb2a3b1dd72c3d28682ec.mp4?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Training Guards</h2>There are four types of guards to train: Warrior, Bowman, Wizard, and Priest. Each type of guard has its own specialty, and you can win by matching different types of guards to maximize your defense.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/ef915e306e7641559bec449a4d638fb9.poster.avif?t=1718959856\" width=640 height=376 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2712570/extras/ef915e306e7641559bec449a4d638fb9.webm?t=1718959856\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i